<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.7.1">
<l>kaṇṇār kaṭalpōl tirumē ṉikariyāy</l>
<l>naṇṇār muṉaiveṉ ṟikoḷvār maṉṉunāṅkūr</l>
<l>tiṇṇār matiḷcūḻ tiruveḷ ḷakkuḷattuḷ</l>
<l>aṇṇā vaṭiyē ṉiṭaraik kaḷaiyāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Dark one whose divine body is like the spacious sea,</l>
<l>Lord in Tiruveḷḷakkuḷam surrounded by sturdy walls</l>
<l>In Nānkūr where dwell those who gain victory</l>
<l rend="indent">[over] their enemies at the battlefront,</l>
<l>Cast off the suffering of your servant, me!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
